attempts.raw_output:
The functionality to import connections from a CSV file is already implemented in the application. The `MRemoteNGCsvImporter` class handles CSV importing, and it is accessible via the "File -> Import" menu (filtering for `*.csv`) as well as through the "Import from Remote Desktop Manager CSV" option. The importer uses `CsvConnectionsDeserializerMremotengFormat` which supports auto-detection of delimiters and mapping of columns based on headers.
